blog.name: electricdreame
blog.title: Devour Your Gods
blog.description:
•Kara • 22 • Brazil • Bi• 
"Fuck me. I'm so tired of being me. Me beautiful. Me ugly. Blonde. Brunette. A million fucking fashion makeovers that only leave me trapped being me.
Who I was before is just a story now. Everything before now, before now, before now, is just a story I carry around. I guess that would apply to anybody in the world. What I need is a new story about who I am.
What I need to do is fuck up so bad I can't save myself."

summary:
Behold: my Spidersona
His name is Potato-Spider, and he got bitten by a radioactive spider right before he could be cut up and...
body:
Behold: my Spidersona

His name is Potato-Spider, and he got bitten by a radioactive spider right before he could be cut up and boiled for soup. His new found powers helped him survive the soup boiling and he emerged victorious from his first encounter with death.

He swore he would save any unsuspecting potatoes from the same fate, and thus took on the Spider mantle.

Feel free to draw fan art of my Spidersona but please credit me!
